{{Ẓeṛ taynisemt|Ungal}}
[[File:Fragonard, The Reader.jpg|thumb|''[[Tin i t-ɣren]]'' n [[Jean-Honoré Fragonard|Fragonard]], ɣer 1770, yellan di National Gallery of Art, Washington.]]

'''Ungal''' d [[tawsit taseklant]], yetwaɛqilen s [[allas]] [[Tasugna|asugnan]]. Amur ameqran yettwaǧǧan i tasugint yeteffɣed seg kra n tinfaliyin am « D ungal ! » neɣ deg kra n inumak n urbib « aneglan » yetceggɛen ar ufeɣnami n udmawen, n lḥalat neɣ n tiddest. 

Ungal, yettwarun di tamezwarut s ifyar n [[taseɣrut]] deg {{s-|XII}} uqbel ad yettwaru s [[tasrit]] deg tazwara n {{s-|XIII}}, yetsbadu daɣen s userken ines ar [[taɣuri]] tamsimant, d amgerrad s [[tamacahut]] neɣ s [[taḥkayt]] yellan deg taneṣlit d [[Ansay atlay|asɣelyazen atlay]].
